\f0\fs30 \cf0 Regardless of ensemble, Campbell\'92s primary objective has always been to get people dancing to melodic representations that bob and weave through all of life\'92s intricacies and emotions. Whether it\'92s utilizing big beats, composing smooth melodies, and working within flowing chord structures, TNERTLE will connect with listeners who want to let loose and have no preconceived notions of how life is suppose to be or where it\'92s going to take you. Go with the flow and you can ensure that you\'92ll have the time of your life.}